description: OPEN HOUSE: Sat. 2/15, 12:15-1:15PM!  224 W 9th, luxury NEW CONSTRUCTION ready for occupancy! Unit 3 is a 2 Bed + Office/2 Bath, 1170 +/- sq ft with Private Deck + DEEDED GARAGE Parking. Ideal location, steps from Washington Village, South Boston's Waterfront and multiple public transportation options! Large open concept living with soaring ceilings and oversized windows throughout. Kitchen features Quartz peninsula with seating for 3-4, slab cabinetry and Fisher/Paykel appliance package. Kitchen opens to living/dining area with private deck off front of unit, perfect for entertaining. Office off living area. Large Primary Bedroom with walk in closet + en suite bath, double vanity + oversized tiled glass shower. Large guest bedroom + guest bath. Hardwood throughout. In-unit washer/dryer and central AC. Professional management. Easy to show!
